'''牛虎铜案'''是1972年在[[中国|中国]][[云南省|云南省]][[玉溪市|玉溪市]][[江川县|江川县]][[李家山古墓群|李家山古墓群]]第24号墓中出土的一件[[青铜器|青铜器]]，为古代[[祭祀|祭祀]]时盛牛羊等祭品的器具。整个青铜器高43厘米，长76厘米，重17公斤<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 玉溪新闻网 | title = 牛虎铜案 | url = http://www.yxdaily.com/yxnews/styx/yxgg/2006_12_22/125743.shtml | date = 2006-12-22 | accessdate = 2011-10-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081202004911/http://www.yxdaily.com/yxnews/styx/yxgg/2006_12_22/125743.shtml | archivedate = 2008-12-02 }}</ref>。整体形象为一站立的大牛，大牛腹中空，内立一小牛。大牛后部有一猛虎咬住牛尾，四爪抓住大牛的后胯<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 人民网 | title = 滇文化的佳作——牛虎铜案（博物一览） | url = http://www.people.com.cn/GB/paper39/8232/776319.html | date = 2003-03-13 | accessdate = 2011-10-25 | archive-date = 2019-06-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190608064837/http://www.people.com.cn/GB/paper39/8232/776319.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。整件青铜器用范模铸造，大牛和虎一次成型，小牛另铸再焊接。现藏于[[云南省博物馆|云南省博物馆]]，为该馆镇馆之宝<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynbwg.cn/diancang/?id=156112904&categoryid=87 |title=云南省博物馆 |access-date=2011-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026034028/http://www.ynbwg.cn/diancang/?id=156112904&categoryid=87 |archive-date=2011-10-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
